markets.title: Will average diesel prices be above $5.35?
markets.rules_primary: If the price of diesel "Diesel (On-Highway) - All Types" is strictly greater than $5.35 on November 21, 2022, as reported in the EIA's weekly Weekly Retail Gasoline and Diesel Prices report,  the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: The market will expire at the sooner of the first 10:00 AM ET following the release of the data (which is generally scheduled for Monday evenings), or December 05, 2022. The market will always close at 4:59 PM ET on the day of the expected release of the data.
